{"tid":1476843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動方向】818港共陰謀與癱瘓機場交通","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:05:53.000Z","uid":304602,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"38f9491606684a413f682799878814023d1bf0d3","tid":1476843,"uid":304602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:53:57.000Z","msg":"P牌仔，<br />\n<br />\n818維園塞唔落20萬人，人咪逼出街上，港共咪話你非法集結，部署防暴加卧底，引起&ldquo;暴力&rdquo;，咪清您場，此乃陽光下的陰謀。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">怕子彈及催淚彈的市民，怕被防暴警察清場的市民，怕出現暴力的市民，和理非的市民，銀髮族可以點做？<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n以下係我建議的低成本、又安全的抗爭方法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應對方法</span></strong>，&quot;打蛇七寸&quot;，癱瘓機場交通，機場癱瘓一日，空運貨值損失101億。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">各位可以用機鐵來回博覽館行、機鐵來回青衣行、東涌線來回欣澳行、用機場巴士來回行、去機場自駕一日遊。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">毋須進入機場大樓亦可癱瘓機埸運作，</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位請遵守機場禁制令</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人有使用公共交通工具及道路的自由。</span></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n各位可參考<br />\n我係空管主任，我想講今日機場真係呢兩個幾月黎香港人贏得最靚既一仗<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458355</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行動亦配合<br />\n818機場員工罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1403240203337453/posts/2397995943861869?s=1107848617&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1403240203337453%2Fposts%2F2397995943861869%3Fs%3D1107848617%26sfns%3Dmo&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=5d73600c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1403240203337453/posts/2397995943861869?s=1107848617&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"52c2e48850195